{
  "stem": "5188.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "In the meantime, my father had found out that you couldn't take any money out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were rules that you could only leave with 10 marks or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to take any money officially out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Even if they emigrated, they-- they could not take any money out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So somehow he managed to get a sum of money out of Germany into Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And don't ask me how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] There must have been ways, and he found out how to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So we had some money now in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And Aunt Erna spoke to the aunt and uncle-- that is, from her side of the family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "This is my mother's side of the family-- no longer my father's cousin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because Aunt Erna wanted us to come to New York, where she was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She didn't want us to go to Uruguay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She was doing anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So she wrote that if we can manage to get the money that's in Switzerland to the United States, she would put it on the aunt and uncle's name.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they would have enough money, she found out, that it would cover us to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we abandoned Uruguay and tried to get Aunt Rose and Uncle Ike, that's-- Aunt Rose was my grandmother's sister on my mother's side of the family-- and Uncle Ike to make the papers for us, along with Aunt Erna.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She already was working as a housekeeper somewhere in New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- that worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow, they got the papers together without the rich cousins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to go to Stuttgart for the visa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now this happened over the course of 1936, '37.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It all took a lot of time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't happen suddenly.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
